Schwerin, Appellant, v. New York El. Ry. Co. et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. April 14, 1892.) Action by Bernard Schwerin against the New York Elevated Railway Company and others.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O’Brien, J.

No opinion. Order reversed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
